f7a7d195-377f-cf5b-70a5-be6b819019dc	3.0.0	https://docs.airbyte.com/integrations/destinations/redshift-migrations#3.0.0	2024-07-31	Version 3.0.0 of destination-redshift removes support for the "standard inserts" mode. S3 staging was always preferred for being faster and less expensive, and as part of Airbyte 1.0, we are officially removing the inferior "standard inserts" mode. Upgrading to this version of the destination will require a configuration with an S3 staging area.\n	2026-03-24 18:08:08.276359+00	2026-03-24 18:08:08.276359+00	[]	\N
